Yeah so today was really really fun. It started off with me waking up cleaning the house going for walk blah blah blah, then i played some cs and i got accepted to clan (none of u prolly knows what that means but whatever. Then i went to Vanessa's house and watched Black Hawk Down, it was sorta boring but eh i lived.

Then when the fun started happening was when i went to Ambers, i totally kicked their asses at Mario Party (yeah thats right bitches, it doesnt matter when i started playing). Then Amber and i went to fire muster to watch fireworks, later danny and nikki came and Amber and I cuddled and danny and nikki cuddled while fireworks went off. It was quite fun, and Nikki gave me another Hickey, hehe that rhymed...

Yeah i figured out that i like hickey's a lot, i think i would never ever have to have sex as long as i could have that hickey feeling all of the time...

Then i went home and pretended to be home for an hour then left to a party which people were leaving... So we went to Perkins and met Rick, who is like the coolest person. 

All in all good day, its good to know that summer wont be the only source of my fun!

PS i also realized that i was being really stupid yesterday. If my friend wants to keep a secret i shouldnt make him tell it. I feel stupid...
